<div class='slide'>
    <h1>Numerical Operators</h1>
    <!-- XXX this description is bad -->
    An operator produces a result by performing an action or calculation. 
    <br />Some available operators
    <ul>
        <li><code>+</code> &nbsp; Add the left number to the right number</li>
        <ul>
            <li><code>45 + 22</code></li>
            <li><code>my_calc + 18</code></li>
        </ul>
            
        <li><code>-</code> &nbsp; Subtract the right number from the left number</li>
        <ul>
            <li><code>127 - 34</code></li>
            <li><code>current_length - 2</code></li>
        </ul>
        
        <li><code>*</code> &nbsp; Multiply the right number by the left number</li>
        <ul>
            <li><code>3 * 3</code></li>
            <li><code>unit * length</code></li>
        </ul>
        
        <li><code>/</code> &nbsp; Divide the right number by the left number</li>
        <ul>
            <li><code>22 / 11</code></li>
            <li><code>length / 2</code></li>
        </ul>

    </ul>
</div>



